after each sentence

1. *Samo* je ona znala istinu. (Only she knew the truth.)
2. *Sama* je otišla bez pozdrava. (She left alone without saying goodbye.)
3. On je *samo* još jednom pokušao. (He tried just once more.)
4. Naša deca su *sama* počela da se igraju. (Our children started to play by themselves.)
5. *Sam* je sebi postavio to pitanje. (He asked himself this question.)
6. Ona je *sama* otišla u šetnju. (She went for a walk by herself.)
7. *Samo* je još jedan korak. (It's just one more step.)
8. Niko drugi nije znao o ovome, *samo* mi. (No one else knew about it, just us.)